        <h6>July 10</h6>
        <q>Water on the road towards the mountain, restricting access to berry picking (blueberry, cranberry) and fall moose hunting.  The water is caused by runoff from the mountain - fire north of here opened ways for water to come down.</q>

        <p>This change affects hunting and gathering berries. I first started noticing this change in 2004, but now I see it seasonally. This change has a strong effect on safety.</p>
